True BASIC              CURSOR 

The "cursor" _ indicates your current position within a window. When you're
inserting characters, anything you type is inserted just before the cursor.
When you're overtyping, the cursor appears as ş and anything you type
replaces the character at the cursor position.  Press the Ins key to change
from inserting to overtyping and vice versa.

